profile: Serving the Muskoka area since 1983...a family business...we continually upgrade our skills and our product knowledge to better serve our clients...we clean residential and industrial carpeting and upholstery, oriental rugs and area rugs..we service all of Muskoka and from Severn Bridge north to Burks Falls area and west to Mactier and east to Carnarvon area....we specialize in pet odour removal...we have the latest fabric protector which not only repels oil and water based stains, but also has UV protecton built in...our carpet protector also repels oil and water based stains and also improves you vacuume performance...we use truck mounted equipment and take extra care in extracting our cleaning solution so that your carpet will dry in hours, not days...also available...island cleaning using our industrial sized portable equipment....call for more information with no obligation.. call 705-646-5640 or text 705-205-1948 or email norm@naturalnorth.com
